{"title":"中山公园一角——儿童游戏场——（首都速写之五）（图片）","authors":["邵宇"],"dates":[{"year":1951,"month":5,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"中山公园一角"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——儿童游戏场—— （首都速写之五）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邵宇  作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们做着游戏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里充满愉快，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们唱着《东方红》，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们生长在毛泽东的年代！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈去看一贯道罪证展览会去啦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈说一会就回来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈要把敌人认清楚看明白。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爸爸、妈妈都说过："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好日子才开头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不许敌人破坏！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不让敌人存在！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}